These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: camping, chess, drawing, reading
Game: canasta, backgammon, scrabble, go
1. Hobby:drawing is between Game:scrabble and Game:backgammon##2
2. Hobby:reading is on the left or right of Game:scrabble##3
3. Game:scrabble is not to the left of Game:scrabble##8
4. Game:backgammon != Hobby:drawing##6
5. Hobby:drawing is somewhere to the right of Hobby:camping##5
6. Hobby:camping is on the right of Game:canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Game   | canasta | scrabble   | go  | backgammon |

